      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Trim the green stalk[s] off your<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> and cut into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p>",
