    {
      "instruction": "<p>Break your <strong>lasagne sheets </strong>into medium-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>lasagne pieces</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, stirring to separate the pieces (this prevents them from sticking together!)</p><p>Cook for 5-7 min stirring occasionally, until slightly tender but not soft</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> lasagne pieces</strong>, rinse under <strong>cold running water</strong>, gently separate the pieces, then leave to drain fully</p>",
