    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lasagne pieces are cooking, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1673431359348-x200.jpg",
