            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [260ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir in your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673431366104-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673431366104-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673431366104-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673431366104-x1000.jpg",
