          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1673431366104-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>aubergine </strong>and cook for 6-8 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once soft, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>,<strong> spinach</strong> and a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until the spinach is beginning to wilt</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1673431374768-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1673431374768-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
