            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Leave the <strong>messy aubergine & spinach lasagne</strong> to stand for 5 min before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
